    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle offers a harmonious balance of performance and reliability. Meticulously maintained to ensure mechanical integrity, it features a well-preserved interior and a refined exterior profile. This selection represents a sophisticated opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a dependable, high-caliber driving experience.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! This car is in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out for a fun weekend getaway, it's ready to roll. It's been well-cared for and runs like a charm. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it handles. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presenting a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This driver-focused example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential. The chassis remains taut with documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and shim-and-bucket valve adjustment, ensuring the high-revving powerplant pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Finished in Carbon Black over a well-preserved Nappa leather interior, this vehicle balances raw analog performance with daily usability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Reliable performance. Clean title. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-maintained daily driver, offering a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, showing only the minor, superficial stone chips on the front bumper typical of careful highway commuting. All body panels are straight with consistent gaps. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery remains supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all original floor mats are included. Every electronic feature, from the responsive touchscreen interface to the heated seats and dual-zone climate control, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a complete service history. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts are crisp and seamless, and the suspension provides a smooth, rattle-free ride. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the brakes and tires have significant life remaining. This car is turn-key ready for its next journey.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for the discerning driver. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and optimal performance. Boasting a clean history and a refined interior, it offers a superior driving experience that balances reliability with executive-level comfort. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber automobile at a competitive valuation.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home. This car has been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of love here and there, but it runs like a dream and is ready to hit the road for many more miles. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is perfect for anyone looking for a dependable, comfy drive. Come take a look\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s performance machine, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L straight-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The powertrain delivers linear torque across the rev range, coupled with a robust limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced subframe and precise suspension geometry that maintains the car's legendary handling characteristics. With its high-revving 8,000 RPM redline and crisp mechanical feedback, this example offers an authentic, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 36800.0,
